articles.title: Will Smith eating spaghetti and other weird AI benchmarks that took off in 2024 - TechCrunch
articles.description: Weird AI benchmarks like Will Smith eating spaghetti, Pictionary, and Minecraft blew up in 2024. But why, exactly?
articles.content:
When a company releases a new AI video generator, it’s not long before someone uses it to make a video of actor Will Smith eating spaghetti.
